{
  "stem": "26111.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was the only country-- and this needs to be said-- the only country at that time that made this-- England was the only country that made this gesture that saved, at the very least, 10,000 lives.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And for that I have always-- in England, out of England-- I have always had a very thankful feeling and respectful feeling for, for the English.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The lower limit, I can't say.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From observation and from memory, I would say seven or eight.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe it was six.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The upper limit was 16.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That I recall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But most of us were sort of in between-- between, I would say, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 9 to 13, 10 to 13, 14.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Um, well, this is a funny thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the Kindertransport [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Association was formed in England-- a few years ago, on the 50th anniversary-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] at that time I was asked the same question.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, I just remember boys!",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember girls.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I have nothing against girls, believe me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was not-- I had not the, the maybe typical, at a certain age, aversion to-- oh, girls!",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No, that was never the case with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I would have known.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And yet, everybody assures me that they were all mixed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I, I can't answer that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All I can say is, as far as I know we were all boys.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That particular transport was all boys.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There may have been others that were mixed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it turns out that this was the first one that-- the first transport that left.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To my knowledge, they were all Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[DRINKS] We were-- had been limited, by the government, to one suitcase each.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
